-eras-tour-biggest-ever-opening-weekend-concert-film-3515544">演唱会影片有史以来首周末票房最高的</a>纪录。碧昂斯本人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/taylor-swift-joined-by-beyonce-the-eras-tour-film-premiere-3513703">出席了《Eras》首映式</a>，斯威夫特称这位休斯顿歌手为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-says-beyonce-has-been-a-guiding-light-throughout-my-career-3514763">“指路明灯”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-to-get-tickets-for-beyonces-renaissance-concert-film-3541400">如何获得碧昂斯 RENAISSANCE 演唱会电影门票的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
