s Addiction 后，在 Welcome To Rockville 音乐节上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/perry-farrells-porno-for-pyros-reunite-at-welcome-to-rockville-3231674">26 年来首次在舞台上重聚</a>。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad2 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p>他们还在洛杉矶进行了一场头条表演，一场亲密的 Lollapalooza <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-porno-for-pyros-play-deep-cuts-for-first-time-in-25-years-3281216">演出结束后</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-janes-addiciton-reunite-to-perform-for-lollapalooza-2719755">在法雷尔创办的音乐节的主舞台上进行了表演</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-future-islands-and-more-for-bearded-theory-2024-buy-tickets-3527883">《Jane&#39;s Addiction》已宣布成为 Bearded Theory 2024 的头条新闻，并在英国独家演出</a>。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-announce-2024-farewell-tour-and-new-ep-3541341">Porno For Pyros 宣布 2024 年告别巡演和新 EP</a>首发于<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> 。</p> ;
